data.description: This home is a gem and recently had a price improvement for a quick sale. THE SELLER IS MOTIVATED!! Come and see your dream home with this 4 bed, 2 bath home. Inside, you'll find a welcoming living area with tall vaulted ceilings, which is perfect for gatherings and entertaining, a split floor plan which offers both space and versatility. The fenced in yard provides privacy, security and safety for your loved ones and pets. This home combines comfort and space. Don't miss the chance to make this your home!
